    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my awesome car! It\u2019s been such a reliable ride and is in really solid shape, perfect for someone who wants a dependable vehicle without the brand-new price tag. It looks great, drives smoothly, and I\u2019ve genuinely enjoyed every mile in it. I\u2019m sad to see it go, but I\u2019m excited for it to bring some joy to its next owner. Drop me a message if you want to take a look\u2014I'd love to show it to you!",
      "price": 29500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 29
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a driver-focused example featuring a high-revving naturally aspirated powerplant mated to a precise short-throw manual gearbox. This vehicle maintains excellent mechanical compression and robust oil pressure across the powerband. The chassis dynamics are sharpened by a limited-slip differential and a well-sorted multi-link rear suspension, ensuring neutral handling and communicative feedback. Recent service includes a comprehensive fluid flush and an inspection of the bushings and subframe mounts. While showing minor signs of road use consistent with its age, the aerodynamic profile remains clean and the structural rigidity is uncompromised. A turn-key performance machine for the discerning enthusiast who prioritizes drivetrain health and kinetic response.",
      "price": 38500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 29
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Used car. Good condition. Well-maintained. Clean title. Runs well. No mechanical issues.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
